[3] Cholera - Somalia (Galguduud)
Date: Tue 21 Oct 2008
Source: Press TV Iran [edited]
<http://www.presstv.ir/detail.aspx?id=72854Â§ionid=351020501>


The Press TV correspondent in South Mogadishu reported on Tuesday [21
Oct 2008] that about 15 people died of cholera in Cabudwaaq town of
the Galguduud region due to lack of clean drinking water and
medicines to treat the disease.

